vote.title: Adopt a resolution authorizing the City Manager to execute an Interlocal Agreement between the City of Dallas and Dallas Area Rapid Transit (DART) for the prohibition of freight services on DART’s Cotton Belt Line of approximately a three-mile section from the Dallas City Limit at the Dallas North Tollway to the Dallas City Limit west of Waterview Parkway - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
